    {
      "chinese": "「青春」意味著甘願放棄溫馨浪漫的愛情去闖蕩生活。沒有怯懦、羞澀和喪志，而是充滿了勇氣、力量和積極。",
      "ab": "Ona “kakapahan” hananay i, o todong to nipiliyas to dihekoay, rihadayay a ’orip, mitanam to kacifaloco’an niira a cingohahay a ’orip. Awaay ko talaw, ngodo^ ato toled, matomes no ’icel ato kalim to kacifaloco’an a ’orip. ",
